## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c514d-102">Quando sono abilitate le smart Label, il grafico riposiziona sovrapposizione delle etichette punti dati, in base a un set di regole definite dall'utente.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-102">When smart labels are enabled, the chart repositions overlapping data point labels, based on a set of user-defined rules.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c514d-103">Linee di callout verranno disegnate per collegare l'etichetta con il punto dati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-103">Callout lines will be drawn to link the label with its data point.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c514d-104">È possibile controllare gli attributi visivi della linea di callout.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-104">The visual attributes of the callout line can be controlled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c514d-105">Questi attributi visivi includono colore, stile di linea e spessore di linea.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-105">These visual attributes include color, line style, and line width.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c514d-106">Il <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A> e <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> proprietà controllano gli abbellimenti, ad esempio le frecce che alla fine della linea di callout.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-106">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> properties control the embellishments, such as arrowheads, that appear at the end of the callout line.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c514d-107">Il <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineColor%2A> proprietà può essere impostata su qualsiasi <xref:System.Drawing.Color> oggetto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-107">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineColor%2A> property can be set to any <xref:System.Drawing.Color> object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c514d-108">Se si imposta il colore della linea di callout, si imposterà automaticamente anche il colore del <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> e l'ornamenti definito dal <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-108">If you set the color of the callout line, you will also automatically set the color of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> and the embellishment defined by the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c514d-109">Il <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineWidth%2A> proprietà controlla la larghezza in pixel della linea di callout.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-109">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineWidth%2A> property controls the pixel width of the callout line.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c514d-110">Utilizzo di questa proprietà ridimensionerà anche gli abbellimenti delle proprietà di <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> e <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-110">Use of this property will also scale the embellishments of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> and the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c514d-111">Lo spostamento delle smart Label può essere controllato tramite l'utilizzo di diverse proprietà correlate movimento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-111">The movement of smart labels can be controlled through the use of several motion-related properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c514d-112">Questi definiscono le regole di spostamento per la direzione, distanza e se il punto dati etichetta è possibile lasciare l'area del tracciato.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-112">These define the rules of movement for the direction, distance and whether the data point label is allowed to leave the plotting area.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c514d-113">Le regole predefinite per lo spostamento verranno risolto in genere la maggior parte dei problemi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-113">The default movement rules will normally resolve most issues.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c514d-114">Il <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> definisce un valore che specifica la distanza massima in pixel, dai dati punto che le etichette dei punti dati possono essere spostate in caso di sovrapposizione.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-114">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> defines a value that specifies the maximum distance in pixels from the data point that data point labels are allowed to be moved in case of overlapping.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c514d-115">Il <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> proprietà definisce un valore che specifica la distanza minima in pixel, dai dati punto che le etichette dei punti dati verranno spostate in caso di sovrapposizione.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-115">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> property defines a value that specifies the minimum distance in pixels from the data point that data point labels will be moved in case of overlapping.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c514d-116">Quando un punto dati etichetta deve essere riposizionata, l'etichetta verrà spostata di almeno il numero di pixel specificato.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-116">When a data point label needs to be repositioned, the label will be moved by at least the number of pixels specified.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c514d-117">Il <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> proprietà indica se le etichette sono nascoste quando non sono possibile risolti i problemi di sovrapposizione.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-117">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> property indicates whether the labels are hidden when overlapping issues cannot be resolved.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c514d-118">Se il <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> proprietà `true`, e il punto dati non può essere disegnato all'interno dell'area specificata da <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> e <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> nelle direzioni consentite da <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>, non essere disegnato etichetta punto dati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-118">If the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> property is `true`, and the data point cannot be drawn within the area specified by <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> in the directions allowed by <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>, the data point label will not be drawn.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c514d-119">Il <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A> proprietà definisce la direzione in cui può essere spostata l'etichetta del punto dati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-119">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A> property defines the direction(s) in which the data point label can be moved.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c514d-120">Questa proprietà accetta uno <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> valore o un OR bit per bit di più <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> valori.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-120">This property accepts one <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> value or a bitwise-OR of multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> values.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c514d-121">Il valore predefinito è l'OR bit per bit di tutti <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> valori, per consentire il riposizionamento in tutte le direzioni possibili tranne che punto al centro dei dati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-121">The default is the bitwise-OR of all <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> values, to allow repositioning in all possible directions except to the center of the data point.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c514d-122">Le Smart Label non sono supportati per i tipi di grafico seguenti:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-122">Smart labels are not supported for the following chart types:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="c514d-123">Grafici a barre: barra e grafici a barre in pila 100%.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-123">Bar charts: bar and hundred-percent-stacked bar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="c514d-124">I grafici con forme: a torta, ad anello, polare e radar.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-124">Shape charts: pie, doughnut, polar and radar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="c514d-125">Grafici a intervallo: intervallo, istogramma con intervalli e i grafici a barre intervallo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-125">Range charts: range, range column and range bar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="c514d-126">Area in pila: in pila di area e grafici ad area in pila 100%.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c514d-126">Stacked area charts: stacked area and hundred-percent-stacked area charts.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```vb  
Imports System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting  
  
Private Function SetSmartLabelsOptions()  
  
   ' Enabling the SmartLabels™ attribute.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.Enabled = true  
  
   ' Set the callout style.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutStyle = LabelCalloutStyle.Underlined  
  
   ' Set the callout line color.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineColor = Color.Goldenrod;  
  
   ' Set the callout line style.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineStyle = ChartDashStyle.Dash  
  
   ' Set the callout line width.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineWidth = 3   
  
   ' Set the callout line anchor cap.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineAnchorCap = LineAnchorCap.Arrow  
End Function  
```  
  
```csharp  
using System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting  
  
private void SetSmartLabelsOptions()  
{  
   // Enabling the SmartLabels™ attribute.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.Enabled = true;  
  
   // Set the callout style.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutStyle = LabelCalloutStyle.Underlined;  
  
   // Set the callout line color.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineColor = Color.Goldenrod;  
  
   // Set the callout line style.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineStyle = ChartDashStyle.Dash;  
  
   // Set the callout line width.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineWidth = 3;  
  
   // Set the callout line anchor cap.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineAnchorCap = LineAnchorCap.Arrow;  
}  
```
